{"tid":1532580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十點鳩嗌心路歷程 有無人同我一樣？","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:13:52.000Z","uid":103040,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"879c42e447c3fcda762b8a0977c0d0dc3b81b133","tid":1532580,"uid":103040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:31:51.000Z","msg":"第1,2晚聽到其他人嗌，都唔夠膽應。<br />\n<br />\n第3,4晚終於夠膽踏出第一步，應左之後手心冒汗，緊張面紅。<br />\n<br />\n第5,6晚鼓氣勇氣嗌出一句香港人，有人回應加油，感動到流淚。<br />\n<br />\n第7晚已經乜都唔怕，望住個鐘倒數十點，一齊嗌，開始認得每晚同你一唱一和既鄰居、同路人把靚聲。<br />\n<br />\n最後想同所有嗌過既人講，雖然唔知你地係邊個，雖然有時會走音，有時會聲沙，但敢發聲既你地，把聲係最好聽架！香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"87a2a5446ca276b3343ae6b69af7c58ce216b5a2","tid":1532580,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"多謝手足晚晚支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087a038eef4d2523aa922c8b75fe21aa58e80a45","tid":1532580,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"［抗爭方程式］和理非 定死線 勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532597</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e2be2837b195fe5c7a0a7130d91586ef8ef835a","tid":1532580,"uid":103040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87a2a5446ca276b3343ae6b69af7c58ce216b5a2","tid":1532580,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:38:28.000Z","msg":"多謝手足晚晚支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"聽到愈黎愈多人，真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2945b6e02e59816a9b07cccce03a83853398725e","tid":1532580,"uid":8204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係嗌到走音嗌到聲沙果堆"},{"pid":"6c788c4718c08c9bb75774272697a696a8d09aba","tid":1532580,"uid":103040,"like":0,"d